\/a>, and the first <a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Judaism\" title=\"Judaism\">Jewish<\/a> Nobel laureate.<\/p>","name":"Paul Johann Ludwig Heyse","place_of_birth":"Berlin ,  Germany","place_of_death":"Munich ,  Germany","text":"Paul Johann Ludwig Heyse , Literature, 1910","year":1910.0}